     │ Immediately see: grade levels,  │ /educators              │ "Does this fit
     │ lesson plans, learning objects  │                         │ my curriculum?"
     │                                 │                         │
  3  │ Browse by grade level or topic  │ /educators/high-school  │ Shopping: "Which
     │ Find lesson plan that fits      │ or /educators/university│ unit does this
     │                                 │                         │ support?"
     │                                 │                         │
  4  │ Preview lesson plan             │ Lesson plan page        │ Assessing:
     │ See: objectives, timing,        │                         │ "Can I use this
     │ materials, discussion questions │                         │ Thursday?"
     │                                 │                         │
